# Goal
Create E2E tests for all authentication flows including Cloudflare Access.

# Auth Flows to Test

## 1. Initial Authentication
- Unauthenticated user visits protected route
- Redirect to Cloudflare Access
- OAuth flow completion
- Return to original destination
- Session cookie set

## 2. Session Persistence
- Refresh page retains auth
- New tab uses existing session
- Session survives browser restart (within limits)

## 3. Session Expiry
- Session expires after timeout
- User notified of expiry
- Graceful redirect to login
- Return to previous page after re-auth

## 4. Protected Route Access
